    "data": "اَلسَّلاَمُ عَلَيْکُمْ يَا خُزَّانَ عِلْمِ اللهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ عَلَيْکُمْ يَا تَرَاجِمَةَ وَحْیِ اللهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ عَلَيْکُمْ يَا اَئِمَّةَ الْهُدٰی اَلسَّلاَمُ عَلَيْکُمْ يَا اَعْلاَمَ التُّقٰی اَلسَّلاَمُ عَلَيْکُمْ يَا اَوْلاَدَ رَسُوْلِ اللهِ اَنَا عَارِفٌ بِحَقِّکُمْ مُسْتَبْصِرٌ بِشَانِکُمْ مُعَادٍ لِاَعْدَآئِکُمْ مُوَالٍ لِاَوْلِيَائِکُمْ باَبِیْ اَنْتُمْ وَ اُمِّیْ صَلَوَاتُ اللهِ عَلَيْکُمْ اَللّٰهُمَّ اِنِّیْ اَتَوَالیٰ اٰخِرَهُمْ كَمَا تَوَالَيْتُ اَوَّلَهُمْ وَ اَبْرَءُ مِنْ کُلِّ وَلِيْجَةٍ دُوْنَهُمْ وَ اَکْفُرُ بِالْجِبْتِ وَ الطَّاغُوْتِ وَ اللَّاتِ وَ الْعُزّٰی صَلَوَاتُ اللهِ عَلَيْکُمْ يَا مَوَالِیَّ وَ رَحْمَةُ اللهِ وَ بَرْكَاتُهٗ اَلسَّلاَمُ عَلَيْكَ يَا سَيِّدَ الْعَابِدِيْنَ وَ سُلاَلَةَ الْوَصِيِّيْنَ اَلسَّلاَمُ عَلَيْكَ يَا بَاقِرَ عِلْمِ النَّبِيِّيْنَ اَلسَّلاَمُ عَلَيْكَ يَا صَادِقًا مُصَدَّقًا فِی الْقَوْلِ وَ الْفِعْلِ يَا مَوَالِیَّ هٰذَا يَوْمُکُمْ وَ هُوْ يَوْمُ الثُّلَثَآءِ وَ اَنَا فِيْهِ ضَيْفٌ لَکُمْ وَ مُسْتَجِيْرٌ بِکُمْ فَاَضِيْفُوْنِیْ وَ اَجِيْرُوْنِیْ بِمَنْزِلَةِ اللهِ عِنْدَکُمْ وَ اٰلِ بَيْتِکُمُ الطَّيِّبِيْنَ الطَّاهِرِيْنَ.\nASSALAAMO A’LAYKUM YAA KHUZZAANA I’LMIL LAAHE ASSALAAMO A’LAYKUM YAA TARAAJEMATA WAHYIL LAAHE ASSALAAMO A’LAYKUM YAA A-IMMATAL HODAA ASSALAAMO A’LAYKUM YAA AA’LAAMAT TOQAA ASSALAAMO A’LAYKUM YAA AWLAADA RASOOLIL LAAHE ANAA A’AREFUN BEHAQQEKUM MUSTABSERUN BESHAANEKUM MOA’ADIN LEAA’DAAAEKUM MOWAALIN LEAWLEYAAAEKUM BEABEE ANTUM WA UMMEE SALAWAATUL LAAHE A’LAYKUM ALLAAHUMMA INNEE ATAWAALAA AAKHERAHUM KAMAA TAWAALAYTO AWWALAHUM WA ABRAO MIN KULLE WALEEJATIN DOONAHUM WA AKFORO BILJIBTE WAT TAAGHOOTE WAL LAATE WAL UZZAA SALAWAATUL LAAHE A’LAYKUM YAA MAWAALIYYA WA RAHMATUL LAAHE WA BARAKAATOHU ASSALAAMO A’LAYKA YAA SAYYEDAL A’ABEDEENA WA SOLAALATAL WASIYYEENA ASSALAAMO A’LAYKA YAA BAAQERA I’LMIN NABIYYEENA ASSALAAMO A’LAYKA YAA SAADEQAN MOSADDAQAN FIL QAWLE WAL FE’LE YAA MAWAALIYYA HAAZAA YAWMOKUM WAHOWA YAWMUS SOLASAAA-E WA ANAA FEEHE ZAYFUN LAKUM WA MUSTAJEERUN BEKUM FAAZEEFOONEE WA AJEEROONEE BEMANZELATIL LAAHE I’NDAKUM WA AALEBAYTEKOMUT TAYYEBEENAT TAAHEREENA.\nPeace be on you, O depositories of Allah’s knowledge! Peace be on you, O commentators of the revealed word of Allah! Peace be on you, O rightly guided Guides unto the true way of life! Peace be on you, O symbols of devotion to duty! Peace be on you, O descendents of the Apostle of Allah! I am aware of your true rights; look at tentively at your refined disposition, full of joy, honour and dignity, take leave and go far away from your enemies, love dearly and keep company of your friends, with my father (I am) at your disposal, and also my mother, blessings of Allah be on you. O my Allah, I willingly submit (out of love and friendship) to all of the minun broken succession, just as You appointed the first of them the “Master”, and I am free from the guilt of taking shelter with any other save them, deny and curse “Jibt” and “Taghoot” “Laat” and “Uzzaa” Blessings of Allah be on you O my beloved Masters! Mercy of Allah be on you, and His blessings. Peace be on you, O pride of worshippers (of Allah) (Zaynul Aabedeen), the founder of the family of the successors (Imaams). Peace be on you, O (Baaqir), he who inherited, knew, and enlarged the knowledge of the Prophets. Peace be on you, O (Saadiq) truthful, his words were true, his deeds were good. O my Masters! Today is your day, Tuesday, in its hours I take refuge with you, and seek your nearness, therefore receive me with open arms, and let me be near you, in the name and for the sake of you belief in Allah, and (belief) of your pure and pious family.", 
    "title": "Ziyarah of Imam Zayn al Abidin, Imam Muhammad al Baqir & Imam Jafar al Sadiq (a) on Tuesday"
